WEBVTT

01:30.840 --> 01:34.970
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.950 --> 01:39.390
[2010]

01:37.950 --> 01:40.070
This company can take care of
household registration.

01:40.070 --> 01:41.530
And this foreign company—

01:41.920 --> 01:43.780
it should pay pretty well, right?

01:44.200 --> 01:45.000
You'd better consider

01:45.000 --> 01:46.060
your grades first.

01:46.229 --> 01:48.479
Everyone wants to get into
those good companies.

01:48.479 --> 01:49.640
It's not that easy.

01:50.310 --> 01:52.039
Wang from the School of Management

01:52.039 --> 01:53.920
requested a song

01:54.070 --> 01:55.400
for the graduating seniors—

01:55.400 --> 01:56.870
"My Future Is Not a Dream."

01:57.039 --> 02:01.150
♪ Are you like me,
lowering your head under the sun? ♪

01:59.350 --> 02:01.280
This song is so old.

02:02.000 --> 02:03.040
I don't want to work hard

02:02.910 --> 02:07.820
♪ Working hard quietly
in streaming sweat ♪

02:03.040 --> 02:04.240
with tears in my eyes.

02:10.400 --> 02:15.280
♪ Are you like me,
even being treated indifferently ♪

02:17.890 --> 02:23.230
♪ Still won't give up the life
you desire ♪

02:20.380 --> 02:23.250
[Episode 10]
[My Future Is Not a Dream]

02:25.280 --> 02:26.340
You are from Yunan?

02:28.960 --> 02:30.490
I know that place very well.

02:30.840 --> 02:32.000
I used to work there.

02:32.630 --> 02:33.760
What a coincidence.

02:36.520 --> 02:38.380
So why did you come to Shengcheng?

02:38.870 --> 02:40.680
My daughter graduated from university.

02:40.680 --> 02:42.030
She wants to start her career
in Shengcheng,

02:42.030 --> 02:43.430
so we came to check it out.

02:43.960 --> 02:45.960
I run a small clothing business.

02:46.420 --> 02:48.079
I was thinking of going to Longcheng
to restock,

02:48.079 --> 02:49.210
so we came together.

02:49.430 --> 02:51.400
You say
your daughter is a university graduate?

02:51.400 --> 02:53.260
That's really quite impressive.

02:54.150 --> 02:55.750
It seems you really have a way

02:55.750 --> 02:56.950
of raising children.

02:57.840 --> 02:59.500
It's mainly to her own credit.

03:02.120 --> 03:02.870
Our Xiaolan

03:02.870 --> 03:03.870
has had it tough.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.910
We are just farmers working the land.

03:06.910 --> 03:08.370
We couldn't help her much.

03:08.400 --> 03:10.080
She relied entirely on herself.

03:10.080 --> 03:11.080
What's wrong with being a farmer?

03:11.080 --> 03:12.520
I come from a farming background too.

03:12.520 --> 03:13.240
Back then,

03:13.240 --> 03:14.240
I worked in Yunan.

03:14.240 --> 03:15.910
There's a lot of delicious food in Yunan,

03:15.910 --> 03:16.910
like mutton soup,

03:17.079 --> 03:17.740
spicy soup,

03:18.000 --> 03:18.910
and pan-fried buns.

03:18.910 --> 03:19.310
Yeah.

03:21.079 --> 03:22.410
Did you call your uncle?

03:22.710 --> 03:23.710
Once Mayor Tang wakes up,

03:23.710 --> 03:25.110
we can go back to the city.

03:25.910 --> 03:26.680
Mayor Tang?

03:27.630 --> 03:28.960
Mr. Tang in there

03:28.960 --> 03:30.960
is the new Vice Mayor of Shengcheng.

03:31.000 --> 03:31.630
Just now, when his driver

03:31.630 --> 03:32.360
was on the phone,

03:32.360 --> 03:33.220
I overheard it.

03:37.120 --> 03:38.150
I'll go pay the fees.

03:38.150 --> 03:38.480
Okay.

03:38.750 --> 03:39.120
Okay.

03:43.470 --> 03:44.120
Mr. Tang,

03:44.150 --> 03:45.880
we brought you some breakfast.

03:46.400 --> 03:46.750
Thank you.

03:46.750 --> 03:47.280
Mrs. Liu.

03:48.590 --> 03:49.120
Alright.

03:50.120 --> 03:51.120
Miss Xia Xiaolan.

03:51.470 --> 03:52.070
Thank you.

03:52.710 --> 03:54.150
We really are fated to meet.

03:54.150 --> 03:56.310
Who would've thought we'd run into
each other again

03:56.310 --> 03:57.870
under these circumstances?

03:57.870 --> 03:58.840
You remember me?

04:00.710 --> 04:01.560
Please, have a seat.

04:01.560 --> 04:01.960
Okay.

04:05.880 --> 04:07.360
That brave and resourceful

04:07.360 --> 04:08.360
young lady

04:08.590 --> 04:09.910
who dared to take on that bad guy

04:09.910 --> 04:10.770
all by herself—

04:10.800 --> 04:12.200
how could I not remember?

04:12.840 --> 04:14.000
I heard from your mother

04:14.000 --> 04:17.070
that you graduated from
Huaqing's Architecture Department.

04:17.070 --> 04:18.360
So why did you come here?

04:18.360 --> 04:20.630
Construction is ongoing everywhere
in Shengcheng.

04:20.630 --> 04:23.070
I'm sure I'll find a place
where my skills can be put to use.

04:23.070 --> 04:24.470
You want to build houses?

04:26.630 --> 04:27.690
You've got no money

04:27.830 --> 04:28.960
and no connections.

04:29.040 --> 04:32.000
You think you can build houses
just because you want to?

04:32.000 --> 04:32.800
Well, right now,

04:32.800 --> 04:34.120
I definitely can't build houses.

04:34.120 --> 04:35.800
But with so many already built,

04:35.800 --> 04:37.190
they'll need interior finishing, right?

04:37.190 --> 04:38.730
I'll start little by little—

04:38.730 --> 04:39.680
one day, I'll have the connections

04:39.680 --> 04:40.680
and the capital.

04:46.240 --> 04:47.190
Do you think Ke Yixiong

04:47.190 --> 04:48.870
is out of his mind?

04:49.270 --> 04:50.680
He asked me to set up a meeting with you

04:50.680 --> 04:53.010
and said he wants to do business together.

04:53.070 --> 04:54.480
He sees you're doing well

04:54.480 --> 04:56.010
and wants a piece of the pie.

04:56.750 --> 04:57.680
But it seems

04:57.680 --> 04:58.920
he has no sense of

04:58.950 --> 05:00.120
his own character.

05:00.630 --> 05:02.070
I'm partnering with you, Sis Bai,

05:02.070 --> 05:03.560
because you have a good character.

05:03.560 --> 05:05.430
But what would I want from Ke Yixiong?

05:05.430 --> 05:07.390
Should I admire the fact that
he once snatched Kang Wei's bag,

05:07.390 --> 05:09.990
or that he tried to abduct me
in broad daylight?

05:13.560 --> 05:15.190
The Longcheng Train Station

05:15.360 --> 05:16.360
is getting more and more chaotic.

05:16.360 --> 05:18.100
It's crawling with Ke Yixiong's men.

05:18.100 --> 05:19.070
Who knows

05:19.120 --> 05:20.480
what other shady business they're up to

05:20.480 --> 05:21.630
besides stealing?

05:22.040 --> 05:22.720
We'd better

05:22.830 --> 05:24.560
stay away from people like him.

05:25.120 --> 05:27.250
But I don't think he's going to give up.

05:27.360 --> 05:28.800
If I really make it big in Shengcheng

05:28.800 --> 05:29.800
in the future,

05:30.190 --> 05:31.680
there'll only be more and more people
getting jealous.

05:31.680 --> 05:32.740
This one. This one.

05:37.310 --> 05:39.510
You look so gorgeous.

05:39.950 --> 05:42.240
This piece's really nice.
When did you buy it?

05:42.240 --> 05:42.870
I see people wearing pretty dresses

05:42.870 --> 05:44.310
all over Shengcheng.

05:44.480 --> 05:45.610
I can't fall behind.

05:46.150 --> 05:47.159
So you really plan

05:47.190 --> 05:49.520
to come to Shengcheng after you graduate?

05:49.600 --> 05:51.240
Actually, the first time
I went to Longcheng

05:51.240 --> 05:51.950
to stock up on goods,

05:51.950 --> 05:53.350
I already made up my mind—

05:53.560 --> 05:54.120
I was definitely

05:54.120 --> 05:55.850
coming here after graduation.

05:56.430 --> 05:57.510
Longcheng is already

05:57.510 --> 05:58.920
quite developed now,

05:59.120 --> 06:00.160
while Shengcheng still has

06:00.160 --> 06:01.190
a lot of room for growth.

06:01.190 --> 06:03.590
So, are you closing your shop
in Jingcheng?

06:04.680 --> 06:06.000
As for my shop in Jingcheng,

06:06.000 --> 06:07.310
I'm leaving it to my aunt.

06:07.310 --> 06:09.680
My mom and I will open a new shop here.

06:10.070 --> 06:10.870
When I go back to Longcheng tomorrow,

06:10.870 --> 06:11.560
I want to visit

06:11.560 --> 06:13.160
the wholesale market again.

06:13.800 --> 06:17.120
But you majored in architecture.
Are you giving up on building houses?

06:17.120 --> 06:18.680
Building houses

06:18.680 --> 06:20.630
requires money and land.

06:20.660 --> 06:21.950
I have neither right now,

06:21.950 --> 06:23.720
so I'll start with what I'm familiar with.

06:23.720 --> 06:24.480
I'll save money

06:24.480 --> 06:25.600
while looking for opportunities.

06:25.600 --> 06:26.040
Got it?

06:26.510 --> 06:28.070
Alright, enough talk about work.

06:28.070 --> 06:30.400
I'm going to take a shower
and get changed.

06:50.510 --> 06:51.570
You look so pretty.

06:52.120 --> 06:52.580
Thanks.

06:53.430 --> 06:54.390
So are you, Sis Bai.

06:54.390 --> 06:55.270
So cool.

06:55.510 --> 06:56.750
Bootlicker.

06:57.159 --> 06:58.820
I mean you're sucking up to me.

06:59.530 --> 07:00.040
Sis Bai.

07:00.190 --> 07:01.720
Where are we going tonight?

07:01.830 --> 07:03.680
I'll show you guys Shengcheng's

07:04.040 --> 07:05.270
most happening spot.

07:06.870 --> 07:07.390
Let's go.

07:07.390 --> 07:07.920
Let's go.

07:22.120 --> 07:22.920
Come on.

07:23.680 --> 07:24.600
What do you think—exciting or not?

07:23.900 --> 07:26.480
♪ It'll be dark in a minute  ♪

07:27.010 --> 07:29.400
♪ Don't rush to success ♪

07:30.840 --> 07:33.230
♪ Time flies so fast like lightning ♪

07:34.210 --> 07:36.330
♪ If you want to be happy,
get out on the streets ♪

07:38.260 --> 07:40.260
♪ No need to turn down the volume ♪

07:40.940 --> 07:43.470
♪ The lamps sway gently in the wind
at dusk ♪

07:44.190 --> 07:47.340
♪ My little beige headphones
blink in comfort ♪

07:48.270 --> 07:50.880
♪ My legs just won't stay still ♪

07:52.670 --> 07:54.670
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

07:54.690 --> 07:56.420
♪ The world keeps spinning ♪

07:56.480 --> 07:58.510
Order whatever you want to eat

07:56.740 --> 07:59.420
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

07:58.510 --> 07:59.870
or drink today.

07:59.920 --> 08:00.720
It's all on me.

08:00.010 --> 08:01.660
♪ Tomorrow seems so far away ♪

08:01.600 --> 08:03.030
You're too generous today, Sis Bai.

08:02.170 --> 08:03.420
♪ Everything is spinning ♪

08:03.560 --> 08:05.190
This is where young people hang out.

08:03.810 --> 08:06.530
♪ Do you want to hold me tight? ♪

08:05.190 --> 08:06.070
It's not expensive.

08:06.070 --> 08:07.000
From what I know about you,

08:06.550 --> 08:10.910
♪ Ho Yuet-tai, Chan Po-lai, Ng Yuen-tsai ♪

08:07.000 --> 08:08.950
this must be your first time here too,
right?

08:08.950 --> 08:10.120
Well, what's fun in

08:10.120 --> 08:10.830
singing and dancing

08:10.830 --> 08:11.510
alone?

08:11.510 --> 08:13.000
It's way better coming with a group.

08:12.110 --> 08:13.690
♪ Ngai Shuk-fai, Szehung Man-wai ♪

08:13.720 --> 08:17.950
♪ Snakes and ants, Lau Ping-tai,
and the Gods combined ♪

08:13.800 --> 08:14.800
Since we're here,

08:14.920 --> 08:16.520
sing us a song. Sing us a song.

08:16.870 --> 08:17.830
I'm not a good singer.

08:17.830 --> 08:19.070
Sing one. Go on.

08:19.190 --> 08:20.390
Don't be nervous, Sis Bai.

08:19.270 --> 08:23.940
♪ All of them start dancing, feet up,
legs turning and heads twisting ♪

08:20.390 --> 08:21.120
My mom says,

08:21.120 --> 08:21.600
when you're nervous,

08:21.600 --> 08:23.120
just pretend the audience are potatoes.

08:23.120 --> 08:23.830
Then you won't be nervous.

08:23.830 --> 08:24.680
I... I'll go pick a song.

08:24.330 --> 08:29.700
♪ Do you wanna dance tonight? ♪

08:24.680 --> 08:25.600
Let's sing together.

08:25.600 --> 08:26.190
Go on. Go on.

08:26.190 --> 08:27.720
-Alright, alright.
-Okay.

08:33.760 --> 08:39.120
♪ Are you like me,
lowering your head under the sun? ♪

08:41.030 --> 08:46.650
♪ Working hard quietly
in streaming sweat ♪

08:48.600 --> 08:53.910
♪ Are you like me,
even being treated indifferently ♪

08:56.250 --> 09:01.930
♪ Still won't give up the life
you desire ♪

09:02.500 --> 09:08.190
♪ I know my future is not a dream ♪

09:09.250 --> 09:12.150
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

09:13.170 --> 09:15.650
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

09:16.530 --> 09:19.890
♪ My heart dances with hope ♪

09:20.780 --> 09:24.330
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

09:24.350 --> 09:27.640
♪ I live every minute to its fullest ♪

09:27.750 --> 09:28.610
Look, Xiaolan.

09:29.080 --> 09:30.120
These are all private

09:30.120 --> 09:30.870
residences.

09:31.030 --> 09:32.320
Nowadays in Shengcheng,

09:32.320 --> 09:34.030
there are many developers

09:34.030 --> 09:35.480
building this kind of commercial housing,

09:35.480 --> 09:37.080
so the demand for
private interior renovation

09:37.080 --> 09:37.550
is huge.

09:37.870 --> 09:38.270
Okay.

09:38.440 --> 09:39.630
Did you archive these cases?

09:39.630 --> 09:40.120
Yes.

09:40.150 --> 09:41.630
Look, I have the camera with me.

09:41.630 --> 09:42.910
All the photos before renovation,

09:42.910 --> 09:43.960
during the process, and after inspection

09:43.960 --> 09:44.820
are all in here.

09:45.180 --> 09:46.830
[Renmin Bridge Small Commodities Market]

09:50.840 --> 09:52.440
Put the everyday items together,

09:52.440 --> 09:53.600
and group together the ones

09:53.600 --> 09:54.120
with the same price.

09:54.120 --> 09:55.080
It makes it easier for you to track,

09:55.080 --> 09:56.240
and easier for customers to choose.

09:56.240 --> 09:56.670
Got it.

09:57.840 --> 09:59.960
Actually, the appliances
and general goods here

09:59.960 --> 10:01.720
are similar to those in Jingcheng,

10:01.720 --> 10:03.150
but the clothes here

10:03.630 --> 10:05.030
are indeed more stylish.

10:05.840 --> 10:07.080
This city is close to Gangdao,

10:07.080 --> 10:08.750
so there are many merchants
from Gangdao and abroad here.

10:08.750 --> 10:09.440
What they wear and use

10:09.440 --> 10:10.770
influences the locals.

10:10.960 --> 10:11.790
So people here

10:11.870 --> 10:13.270
care more about fashion,

10:13.270 --> 10:14.670
and are more willing to spend on it.

10:14.670 --> 10:16.230
So is it even tougher

10:16.230 --> 10:17.600
for us to open a shop here?

10:17.600 --> 10:18.870
As long as we find

10:18.870 --> 10:20.440
our own niche and specialty,

10:20.440 --> 10:21.370
it won't be hard.

10:27.550 --> 10:29.800
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

10:57.240 --> 10:58.200
But your line of thinking

10:58.200 --> 11:00.240
may not be best for the client.

11:00.790 --> 11:02.510
That's the only way to maximize our odds.

11:02.510 --> 11:03.870
Otherwise, if any step in the process

11:03.870 --> 11:04.550
goes wrong...

11:04.550 --> 11:05.550
Then just make sure

11:05.550 --> 11:06.670
every step is done right!

11:06.670 --> 11:07.550
A case doesn't just

11:07.550 --> 11:08.550
concern the client—

11:08.550 --> 11:09.120
it concerns his entire family.

11:09.120 --> 11:09.550
Hello.

11:10.080 --> 11:10.440
Hello.

11:10.440 --> 11:11.270
Are you looking for someone?

11:11.270 --> 11:12.120
Yes, I'm looking for Mr. Wu Hao.

11:12.120 --> 11:12.750
You should ask yourself

11:12.750 --> 11:14.150
if you really did your best!

11:14.150 --> 11:15.480
He's almost done there.

11:20.410 --> 11:21.800
It's okay. Don't be agitated.

11:21.800 --> 11:22.790
We'll go over it later.

11:22.790 --> 11:23.850
Alright, go ahead.

11:24.320 --> 11:25.790
Mr. Wu Hao isn't big on formalities.

11:25.790 --> 11:27.850
You can go in
as long as his office is empty.

11:27.850 --> 11:28.240
Thanks.

11:28.240 --> 11:28.900
No worries.

11:34.720 --> 11:35.200
Senior.

11:36.360 --> 11:37.090
You're here.

11:37.480 --> 11:38.790
How was it? Was this place hard to find?

11:38.790 --> 11:39.470
No, it was okay.

11:39.470 --> 11:40.240
Come on, sit.

11:41.960 --> 11:43.320
This is how it is here.

11:43.960 --> 11:44.690
Small place,

11:44.840 --> 11:45.770
not many people,

11:46.000 --> 11:47.130
but plenty of cases.

11:47.200 --> 11:48.720
It's a madhouse every day.

11:51.360 --> 11:52.390
A madhouse,

11:52.720 --> 11:53.650
but fulfilling.

11:55.960 --> 11:57.440
You're graduating this year, right?

11:57.440 --> 11:57.790
Yes.

11:58.080 --> 11:59.120
Time flies.

11:59.630 --> 12:00.440
I still remember when you

12:00.440 --> 12:01.910
first joined the Student Union.

12:01.910 --> 12:02.600
It was written all over your face:

12:02.600 --> 12:04.320
"I'm going to do something big."

12:04.320 --> 12:05.360
Actually,

12:05.820 --> 12:07.080
I still think that way.

12:10.270 --> 12:10.840
So,

12:11.700 --> 12:13.480
have you decided where you want to work?

12:13.480 --> 12:15.000
The procuratorate or the court?

12:15.000 --> 12:15.510
With your grades,

12:15.510 --> 12:16.320
plenty of good employers

12:16.320 --> 12:17.720
must be eager to take you.

12:18.870 --> 12:20.320
I do have some options,

12:20.750 --> 12:22.210
but I haven't decided yet.

12:23.030 --> 12:24.030
Find a good employer,

12:24.030 --> 12:25.240
get a stable job,

12:25.600 --> 12:27.460
and your family will feel at ease.

12:27.840 --> 12:29.390
But besides stability,

12:30.080 --> 12:31.680
I want to try something else.

12:34.790 --> 12:35.590
Have some tea.

12:36.540 --> 12:37.600
Your dishes are all served.

12:37.600 --> 12:38.480
-Okay. Thank you.
-Enjoy.

12:38.480 --> 12:39.080
Thank you.

12:40.840 --> 12:42.440
I've discussed it with my mom.

12:42.440 --> 12:44.000
I'll go to Longcheng tomorrow to stock up

12:44.000 --> 12:45.320
and then head back to school,

12:45.320 --> 12:47.260
and she'll stay in Shengcheng
to look for a shop location.

12:47.260 --> 12:48.170
The shop here

12:48.200 --> 12:49.800
will probably be left to her.

12:51.360 --> 12:52.960
Mrs. Liu has changed so much.

12:53.480 --> 12:54.960
I remember
when you first arrived in Shangdu

12:54.960 --> 12:55.840
to open the shop,

12:55.840 --> 12:57.300
she didn't know anything.

12:58.150 --> 12:58.840
Exactly.

12:59.120 --> 13:00.630
Back then, she didn't know
how to style outfits

13:00.630 --> 13:02.240
and barely knew any characters.

13:02.240 --> 13:03.840
Over the years, she's been selling goods
by day

13:03.840 --> 13:05.720
and reading Taotao's textbooks at night.

13:05.720 --> 13:07.200
She knows almost all the characters now.

13:07.200 --> 13:08.200
Starting a business really

13:08.200 --> 13:09.060
helps you grow.

13:09.670 --> 13:10.910
Every environment

13:10.910 --> 13:12.480
has its opportunities and challenges.

13:12.480 --> 13:13.670
It all comes down to what we make of it.

13:13.670 --> 13:14.510
How things turn out ultimately

13:14.510 --> 13:15.770
depends on ourselves.

13:16.630 --> 13:18.240
So you're really not going to stay

13:18.240 --> 13:19.300
for your master's?

13:19.870 --> 13:21.600
I heard the professors at your school

13:21.600 --> 13:23.130
are all hoping you'll stay.

13:23.750 --> 13:25.120
After coming to Shengcheng

13:25.120 --> 13:27.240
and seeing the pace of this place
with my own eyes,

13:27.240 --> 13:28.150
I know that
if I don't get in the game now,

13:28.150 --> 13:29.950
I'll be left behind by the times.

13:30.000 --> 13:31.320
I can no longer sit calmly

13:31.320 --> 13:32.270
in a classroom

13:32.270 --> 13:33.130
and just study.

13:33.750 --> 13:34.360
Besides,

13:34.870 --> 13:35.870
I think this place

13:35.910 --> 13:37.390
is a bigger classroom,

13:37.720 --> 13:38.650
a bigger school.

13:39.070 --> 13:40.240
I can learn properly

13:40.270 --> 13:41.330
through practice.

13:42.390 --> 13:43.790
You're always like this.

13:44.160 --> 13:45.760
You never seem lost

13:46.000 --> 13:46.720
or afraid.

13:50.750 --> 13:51.410
Zhou Cheng.

13:51.870 --> 13:53.480
You went to visit Senior Wu today—

13:53.480 --> 13:54.210
how did it go?

13:55.240 --> 13:55.970
Pretty good.

13:56.910 --> 13:58.080
The law firm isn't big,

13:58.080 --> 13:59.120
and there aren't many people.

13:59.120 --> 14:00.390
It's only been open for 6 months.

14:00.390 --> 14:01.080
It can't compare to

14:01.080 --> 14:02.320
government institutions, of course,

14:02.320 --> 14:03.080
but the work atmosphere

14:03.080 --> 14:03.880
is quite good:

14:04.550 --> 14:05.030
free,

14:05.670 --> 14:06.200
dynamic,

14:06.750 --> 14:07.810
and full of energy.

14:08.030 --> 14:10.360
Just like this city.

14:16.750 --> 14:17.410
Zhou Cheng,

14:18.790 --> 14:21.050
my dream is to be realized in Shengcheng,

14:21.320 --> 14:22.340
but your dream

14:22.550 --> 14:24.350
doesn't necessarily have to be.

14:24.720 --> 14:25.320
Of course,

14:25.630 --> 14:27.430
I want to build a future with you.

14:27.630 --> 14:28.480
But just like

14:28.480 --> 14:29.680
what I told my mother—

14:29.840 --> 14:31.900
we're not accessories to each other.

14:32.000 --> 14:33.270
Don't let me influence

14:33.440 --> 14:35.370
your decisions about your future.

14:39.870 --> 14:41.080
But how can I

14:41.840 --> 14:43.690
not have my future influenced by you?

14:43.690 --> 14:45.150
You are part of my future.

14:45.670 --> 14:46.270
Likewise,

14:46.910 --> 14:47.720
I hope I am

14:48.270 --> 14:49.600
part of your future too.

14:51.030 --> 14:51.550
I know

14:52.270 --> 14:53.360
how you got here

14:53.360 --> 14:54.090
step by step.

14:54.480 --> 14:55.120
I also know

14:55.790 --> 14:56.600
there are things

14:56.600 --> 14:57.930
you urgently want to do.

14:59.030 --> 14:59.960
Romantic relationship isn't

14:59.960 --> 15:01.020
your top priority.

15:01.750 --> 15:02.630
I respect that.

15:04.510 --> 15:05.510
But sometimes,

15:06.600 --> 15:08.000
it acts like a shield

15:08.790 --> 15:09.600
between us.

15:11.320 --> 15:12.120
Every time you face

15:12.120 --> 15:13.200
a choice,

15:14.000 --> 15:16.200
you use it to push me away.

15:20.720 --> 15:21.320
I'm sorry.

15:23.000 --> 15:24.130
Maybe I'm not so sure

15:24.560 --> 15:25.560
about the future,

15:26.360 --> 15:28.870
so I got a bit emotional.

15:30.120 --> 15:30.980
No, Zhou Cheng.

15:31.790 --> 15:33.050
I will think carefully

15:33.150 --> 15:34.280
about what you said.

15:39.440 --> 15:41.100
Excuse me. Make way. Make way.

15:41.120 --> 15:42.050
Coming through.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.410
Not satisfied?

15:51.960 --> 15:53.460
The designs have been upgraded,

15:53.460 --> 15:55.460
but the fabric hasn't changed much.

15:58.440 --> 16:00.270
Is that the Ke Yixiong

16:00.270 --> 16:01.600
Bai Zhenzhu mentioned?

16:02.750 --> 16:04.030
There are inspectors in the market.

16:04.030 --> 16:04.630
It's fine.

16:05.750 --> 16:06.320
Besides,

16:06.610 --> 16:07.480
you're here with me.

16:07.480 --> 16:08.340
I'm not afraid.

16:17.150 --> 16:18.840
This shop looks pretty good.

16:19.390 --> 16:19.870
Really?

16:20.480 --> 16:22.280
Tell me what makes it different.

16:22.600 --> 16:24.060
I can't put my finger on it,

16:24.200 --> 16:25.910
but compared to other shops,

16:26.120 --> 16:27.550
the styles are just better.

16:27.550 --> 16:28.120
Our Zhou

16:28.120 --> 16:29.250
has quite a good eye.

16:34.700 --> 16:35.480
Feel free to look around.

16:35.480 --> 16:37.150
These are all foreign trade goods.

16:37.150 --> 16:37.720
Boss.

16:38.200 --> 16:39.730
This is a silk blend, right?

16:41.240 --> 16:42.700
You know your stuff, Miss.

17:03.940 --> 17:06.190
[Clothing Tycoon Brutally Killed by
His Treacherous Young Wife]

17:07.430 --> 17:08.819
Chen Xiliang?

17:12.880 --> 17:13.810
Yeah, that's me.

17:14.750 --> 17:15.410
You know me?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.030
Let me tell you, Miss,

17:17.030 --> 17:18.160
you have good taste.

17:22.829 --> 17:23.790
Hurry up! Run!

17:28.590 --> 17:29.120
Xiaolan,

17:29.240 --> 17:30.500
why are you still here?

17:30.640 --> 17:31.680
Hey, what happened?

17:31.680 --> 17:32.470
What are you waiting for?

17:32.470 --> 17:33.880
Pack up and run.

17:36.540 --> 17:37.600
Look for yourself.

17:54.760 --> 17:55.590
Let me tell you, Miss,

17:55.590 --> 17:56.720
you have good taste.

17:58.790 --> 17:59.720
So this is

18:00.440 --> 18:01.270
Chen Xiliang,

18:01.270 --> 18:02.510
the clothing tycoon who will one day

18:02.510 --> 18:03.970
meet his end at the hands of

18:04.160 --> 18:05.310
his treacherous young second wife.

18:05.310 --> 18:06.240
This is the first time

18:06.240 --> 18:07.590
I've met someone from my past timeline

18:07.590 --> 18:09.050
who crossed paths with me.

18:09.160 --> 18:11.160
Could it be that
this dream is about to end?

18:11.160 --> 18:11.960
You can buy it as a set.

18:11.960 --> 18:13.400
If you buy the set,
I can give you a discount.

18:13.400 --> 18:14.590
If you don't like this match,

18:14.590 --> 18:15.310
you can swap...

18:15.310 --> 18:16.350
Xiao... Xiaolan.

18:17.640 --> 18:18.770
Not for now, thanks.

18:21.720 --> 18:22.720
Nothing's wrong.

18:26.020 --> 18:27.070
Please come in, come in.

18:27.070 --> 18:27.720
Feel free to look around.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.650
These are all foreign trade goods.

18:36.480 --> 18:38.030
He really is the brother-in-law of

18:38.030 --> 18:39.550
Chenyu Garment Factory's director.

18:39.550 --> 18:41.200
He's been handling foreign trade orders

18:41.200 --> 18:42.530
and recently went solo.

18:42.960 --> 18:44.890
He should be living on this street.

18:45.110 --> 18:46.000
They haven't heard of his family

18:46.000 --> 18:47.460
having any major trouble—

18:47.480 --> 18:48.720
just that his relationship with his wife's

18:48.720 --> 18:49.770
relatives isn't very good,

18:49.770 --> 18:51.300
and they had a few disputes.

18:52.440 --> 18:53.200
Sounds like

18:53.350 --> 18:54.550
he really is that future

18:54.550 --> 18:55.550
clothing tycoon.

18:55.740 --> 18:56.720
There haven't been any

18:56.720 --> 18:58.320
life-or-death situations,

18:58.480 --> 19:00.590
so he probably isn't a transmigrator.

19:00.590 --> 19:02.550
Why did you ask me
to look into Chen Xiliang?

19:02.550 --> 19:03.410
Do you know him?

19:08.550 --> 19:09.950
The goods of the few shops

19:10.400 --> 19:11.590
we just checked out aren't great.

19:11.590 --> 19:13.160
Only his goods stand out—

19:13.160 --> 19:14.550
the styles and fabrics are pretty decent.

19:14.550 --> 19:16.000
So I wanted to see if

19:16.000 --> 19:16.790
he's reliable

19:16.790 --> 19:19.120
and whether I can work with him long-term.

19:19.240 --> 19:20.500
But you ran off so fast—

19:20.790 --> 19:21.640
I bet he thinks

19:21.640 --> 19:23.100
you didn't like his goods.

19:27.070 --> 19:27.880
Ms. Xia.

19:28.510 --> 19:29.790
You're in quite a good mood, huh?

19:29.790 --> 19:31.520
Coming all the way here for tea.

19:32.200 --> 19:34.480
Mr. Ke, you've been following us
for quite a while.

19:34.480 --> 19:35.960
So you finally decided to
come into the open

19:35.960 --> 19:36.760
and talk to me?

19:39.680 --> 19:40.880
So you're Ke Yixiong?

19:43.750 --> 19:46.160
Is this your bodyguard, Ms. Xia?

19:47.480 --> 19:48.880
Yes, he's my bodyguard.

19:50.030 --> 19:51.290
And also my boyfriend.

19:54.270 --> 19:55.470
Pleasure to meet you.

19:56.310 --> 19:56.840
Let's go.

20:01.480 --> 20:03.830
It seems Ms. Bai

20:03.920 --> 20:05.380
didn't pass on my message.

20:06.110 --> 20:06.920
She did.

20:07.590 --> 20:09.390
But I don't want to work with you.

20:09.440 --> 20:11.770
I have no interest in illegal activities.

20:15.270 --> 20:16.740
In broad daylight,

20:17.030 --> 20:19.030
don't go spreading rumors, Ms. Xia.

20:19.160 --> 20:19.880
We

20:20.030 --> 20:22.590
are all law-abiding citizens.

20:23.920 --> 20:24.720
Whether you broke the law or not,

20:24.720 --> 20:26.440
you know perfectly well yourself.

20:26.440 --> 20:27.110
As for the past,

20:27.110 --> 20:28.550
I won't settle the score with you.

20:28.550 --> 20:30.550
From now on, we go our separate ways.

20:31.640 --> 20:32.770
I forgot to mention,

20:32.960 --> 20:34.420
my boyfriend studies law.

20:39.030 --> 20:41.090
Ms. Xia, your business has grown big,

20:41.110 --> 20:41.830
and your way of speaking

20:41.830 --> 20:43.430
is certainly different now.

20:43.590 --> 20:44.960
I know the law, too.

20:44.960 --> 20:46.400
It requires evidence.

20:46.640 --> 20:49.240
You can't make accusations
without evidence.

20:49.240 --> 20:50.030
Since

20:50.240 --> 20:52.030
Ms. Xia looks down on us,

20:53.070 --> 20:53.930
we're leaving.

21:03.680 --> 21:04.240
Miss,

21:04.750 --> 21:06.080
taking the train alone?

21:07.310 --> 21:08.510
Where are you headed?

21:08.590 --> 21:09.200
Home.

21:10.030 --> 21:10.750
Home, huh?

21:11.510 --> 21:12.960
Are you studying in school

21:12.960 --> 21:13.920
or working?

21:18.590 --> 21:19.920
What are you looking at?

21:21.110 --> 21:22.640
Those two are really weird.

21:23.000 --> 21:25.000
They don't look like sisters at all.

21:26.770 --> 21:27.590
Come here, let's talk.

21:27.590 --> 21:28.650
Come here. Come on.

21:32.000 --> 21:32.470
Miss,

21:32.790 --> 21:33.790
traveling alone?

21:34.000 --> 21:35.330
Trying to look for a job?

21:35.680 --> 21:37.210
What kind of job do you want?

21:38.200 --> 21:39.440
That woman is a human trafficker.

21:39.440 --> 21:41.100
She tried to abduct me before.

21:42.400 --> 21:43.060
Abduct you?

21:45.400 --> 21:47.240
I'll find you a place to stay
as soon as we get off.

21:47.240 --> 21:49.170
Then I'll take you to look for a job.

21:49.920 --> 21:50.650
Don't worry.

21:50.750 --> 21:52.200
Leave it all to me.

21:53.170 --> 21:53.960
Where's your ID card?

21:53.960 --> 21:54.790
Let me see.

21:57.110 --> 21:57.570
Come on.

21:58.640 --> 21:59.370
Give it to me.

22:01.960 --> 22:02.400
Miss.

22:02.600 --> 22:03.460
Do you know her?

22:04.350 --> 22:04.960
I...

22:06.030 --> 22:07.160
Who are you?

22:07.590 --> 22:08.690
You don't remember me?

22:08.690 --> 22:09.230
Alright.

22:09.440 --> 22:10.700
Let me jog your memory.

22:11.310 --> 22:11.880
Miss.

22:12.400 --> 22:13.590
Traveling alone by train?

22:13.590 --> 22:14.680
Where are you headed?

22:14.680 --> 22:15.830
Trying to look for a job?

22:15.830 --> 22:17.110
I have connections.

22:17.440 --> 22:18.570
Give me your ID card.

22:18.610 --> 22:19.350
I'll find you a job

22:19.350 --> 22:21.010
as soon as we get off the train.

22:21.370 --> 22:22.030
Is that what she just

22:22.030 --> 22:22.830
told you?

22:25.030 --> 22:25.750
Ma'am.

22:26.080 --> 22:27.110
After all these years,

22:27.110 --> 22:27.880
your tricks for abducting people

22:27.880 --> 22:29.140
haven't changed a bit.

22:29.310 --> 22:30.750
I don't know what you're talking about.

22:30.750 --> 22:31.610
You don't know?

22:32.030 --> 22:32.920
If I hadn't stopped you,

22:32.920 --> 22:33.750
you would've taken

22:33.750 --> 22:34.980
both her and her ID card away, right?

22:34.980 --> 22:36.160
You're slandering an innocent person.

22:36.160 --> 22:37.200
Talking all that nonsense.

22:37.200 --> 22:38.200
An innocent person?

22:38.200 --> 22:39.630
More like a human trafficker!

22:39.630 --> 22:40.590
Wait, what's going on?

22:40.590 --> 22:41.240
Come and look, everyone.

22:41.240 --> 22:43.070
There's a human trafficker here
abducting a young girl.

22:43.070 --> 22:44.640
Don't talk nonsense, you two.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.440
You're wronging an innocent person.

22:45.440 --> 22:46.510
This is my sister.

22:47.110 --> 22:48.400
She's my sister.

22:48.610 --> 22:50.000
What are you all doing?

22:52.200 --> 22:52.730
Is it her?

22:53.310 --> 22:54.110
Yes, it's her.

22:54.200 --> 22:55.060
Do you know her?

22:55.640 --> 22:56.590
Don't say anything out of line.

22:56.590 --> 22:57.590
I was helping you.

22:57.790 --> 22:59.190
She's my younger sister.

22:59.240 --> 23:00.480
When we got on,

23:00.480 --> 23:02.590
she was in a rush and didn't have time
to buy a ticket.

23:02.590 --> 23:03.830
I was just helping her get one. Look.

23:03.830 --> 23:04.960
I was handling that.

23:06.030 --> 23:07.480
She's your younger sister?

23:07.480 --> 23:09.480
Then why did you only buy one ticket
for yourself?

23:09.480 --> 23:10.030
Officer,

23:10.440 --> 23:11.790
this person was acting suspiciously.

23:11.790 --> 23:13.270
Even if she's not a human trafficker,

23:13.270 --> 23:14.030
she's a fare evader.

23:14.030 --> 23:15.270
You're full of nonsense.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.880
I did buy a ticket.

23:16.880 --> 23:18.140
Look carefully, okay?

23:18.160 --> 23:19.380
She's the one evading the fare.

23:19.380 --> 23:20.160
I don't know her.

23:20.160 --> 23:21.110
You don't know her?

23:21.110 --> 23:22.640
Wasn't she your younger sister just now?

23:22.640 --> 23:23.900
Now you don't know her?

23:24.960 --> 23:25.640
Officer,

23:25.880 --> 23:27.410
this is this girl's ID card.

23:27.440 --> 23:28.440
If I hadn't stopped them,

23:28.440 --> 23:29.960
she'd probably be abducted by now.

23:29.960 --> 23:30.960
I just... I...

23:31.000 --> 23:32.310
Alright, stop arguing. Stop it.

23:32.310 --> 23:33.270
Come with me to the dining car.

23:33.270 --> 23:34.110
We'll go to the station at the next stop.

23:34.110 --> 23:35.400
Why should I go?

23:35.400 --> 23:36.070
On what grounds?

23:36.070 --> 23:37.240
Come with me, you all. Move it.

23:37.240 --> 23:37.880
Come with me.

23:37.880 --> 23:38.830
I'm not going. I'm not going.

23:38.830 --> 23:39.920
Passengers on both sides, please sit down.

23:39.920 --> 23:40.790
The railway system

23:40.790 --> 23:41.830
will keep an eye on this person.

23:41.830 --> 23:42.750
There isn't enough evidence this time

23:42.420 --> 23:44.790
[Yuezhou Railway Station Police Station]

23:42.750 --> 23:43.610
to arrest them,

23:43.750 --> 23:45.720
but sooner or later, we'll get evidence.

23:45.720 --> 23:47.050
Thank you for your help.

23:47.110 --> 23:47.920
Take this,

23:47.920 --> 23:49.070
and you can take the next train

23:49.070 --> 23:49.870
to Jingcheng.

23:49.920 --> 23:51.720
Thank you for your hard work, Officer.

23:51.720 --> 23:52.520
Safe travels.

23:53.270 --> 23:53.870
Thank you.

23:54.400 --> 23:55.000
Thank you.

23:55.750 --> 23:57.150
Why don't I see that girl?

23:58.960 --> 23:59.510
Yeah.

23:59.920 --> 24:00.720
I saw her come out,

24:00.720 --> 24:01.960
but I haven't seen her since.

24:01.960 --> 24:02.440
Wait!

24:03.720 --> 24:04.440
Here you are.

24:04.440 --> 24:06.030
Please wait a second, you two.

24:06.030 --> 24:07.360
My name is Ye Xiaoqiong.

24:08.200 --> 24:09.930
Thank you for helping me today.

24:11.390 --> 24:12.030
It's all my fault.

24:12.030 --> 24:13.920
I made you get separated from your friend.

24:13.920 --> 24:14.520
It's okay.

24:14.720 --> 24:15.880
Our friend even asked us

24:15.880 --> 24:17.280
to make sure you're safe.

24:17.720 --> 24:18.320
Thank you.

24:18.440 --> 24:19.370
You're welcome.

24:20.030 --> 24:20.630
By the way,

24:20.920 --> 24:22.680
you paid for my ticket.

24:23.030 --> 24:24.440
I wrote an IOU.

24:24.920 --> 24:25.880
Please take it.

24:29.590 --> 24:31.000
Give me an address,

24:31.590 --> 24:33.030
and I'll pay you back.

24:36.350 --> 24:36.750
Okay.

24:38.070 --> 24:39.200
But the amount

24:39.920 --> 24:40.830
needs to be changed.

24:40.830 --> 24:41.760
Add another 100.

24:50.110 --> 24:51.510
Take this 100 yuan for now.

24:51.510 --> 24:53.110
You can't even afford a ticket.

24:53.110 --> 24:54.920
What if you can't find your family?

24:54.920 --> 24:56.510
How will you get back on your feet
without money?

24:56.510 --> 24:57.030
Take it.

24:57.310 --> 24:58.160
When you have money,

24:58.160 --> 24:59.490
pay me back everything.

25:05.750 --> 25:06.400
Come on.

25:06.880 --> 25:09.210
Don't you even have that much confidence?

25:19.400 --> 25:20.800
You are both good people.

25:21.200 --> 25:21.960
Thank you.

25:23.000 --> 25:24.130
I won't let you down.

25:24.640 --> 25:26.300
I'll definitely pay you back.

25:31.270 --> 25:32.880
I'm a good person?

25:33.830 --> 25:34.720
Wasn't I

25:34.750 --> 25:36.010
super fierce just now?

25:36.160 --> 25:36.720
Yeah.

25:37.790 --> 25:39.320
A super fierce good person.

25:40.070 --> 25:40.600
Let's go.

25:41.030 --> 25:41.560
Let's go.

25:51.550 --> 25:52.940
Comrades, please sit here.

25:52.940 --> 25:53.310
Okay.

25:53.480 --> 25:54.200
Okay, thanks.

25:54.200 --> 25:54.800
Let's sit.

26:04.310 --> 26:04.960
Kang Wei

26:05.160 --> 26:07.640
should have arrived in
Jingcheng by now, right?

26:07.640 --> 26:08.500
He should have.

26:09.160 --> 26:11.220
We won't arrive until noon tomorrow.

26:12.510 --> 26:13.040
Xiaolan.

26:14.400 --> 26:15.460
There's something

26:15.830 --> 26:16.750
I want to make clear

26:16.750 --> 26:18.280
before we reach Jingcheng.

26:21.310 --> 26:22.440
I've made up my mind.

26:23.160 --> 26:24.220
After graduation,

26:24.640 --> 26:25.900
I'll go to Shengcheng.

26:27.400 --> 26:27.750
You...

26:27.750 --> 26:28.680
Just hear me out.

26:29.400 --> 26:30.440
Emotionally,

26:30.640 --> 26:31.200
of course, it's because

26:31.200 --> 26:32.330
I want to be with you.

26:32.720 --> 26:33.790
But this decision I'm making

26:33.790 --> 26:34.520
is rational.

26:35.270 --> 26:35.870
I promise—

26:36.310 --> 26:37.270
I don't feel wronged

26:37.270 --> 26:38.130
or conflicted,

26:38.440 --> 26:40.770
and I'm not sacrificing anything for you.

26:40.920 --> 26:41.640
Back then,

26:42.510 --> 26:43.570
you told Mayor Tang

26:44.110 --> 26:46.720
that you liked
Shengcheng's pace of development

26:46.720 --> 26:48.050
and its opportunities.

26:48.510 --> 26:49.310
Actually,

26:50.160 --> 26:50.830
I didn't really

26:50.830 --> 26:52.160
feel anything at first.

26:53.030 --> 26:53.550
But in

26:53.550 --> 26:54.750
Senior Wu's law firm,

26:55.310 --> 26:56.270
I felt it.

26:57.480 --> 26:58.340
I really like it

26:59.240 --> 27:00.170
and aspire to it.

27:01.240 --> 27:01.900
Zhou Cheng.

27:02.480 --> 27:03.960
About what you said yesterday,

27:03.960 --> 27:05.890
I also thought about it seriously.

27:06.510 --> 27:08.550
My way of thinking and handling things

27:08.550 --> 27:09.830
is a bit different from

27:09.920 --> 27:11.250
most people of this era.

27:12.000 --> 27:13.460
Before, I didn't consider

27:13.510 --> 27:14.510
whether you could

27:14.510 --> 27:15.960
accept the way I behave.

27:16.830 --> 27:17.590
If I made you feel

27:17.590 --> 27:18.400
insecure,

27:18.920 --> 27:19.830
I apologize.

27:20.920 --> 27:21.830
But I promise

27:22.310 --> 27:24.240
I'll try my best to adjust myself
from now on,

27:24.240 --> 27:25.590
so we can stay in sync.

27:26.030 --> 27:26.640
No, no, no.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.240
Yesterday,

27:29.920 --> 27:30.960
I was in a bad mood.

27:31.720 --> 27:32.470
I apologize.

27:34.270 --> 27:34.680
Okay.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.960
Then let's both stop apologizing.

27:36.960 --> 27:38.200
Actually, I think it's good

27:38.200 --> 27:39.480
that we talked things out.

27:39.480 --> 27:41.400
It's better than having differences

27:41.400 --> 27:43.000
and keeping them bottled up.

27:44.400 --> 27:45.260
But Zhou Cheng,

27:46.110 --> 27:47.110
I never intended

27:47.110 --> 27:48.110
to push you away.

27:49.200 --> 27:50.030
I shared

27:50.400 --> 27:52.070
my life plans with you

27:52.480 --> 27:53.550
because I hope

27:54.110 --> 27:55.030
my plans

27:55.590 --> 27:57.250
can be compatible with yours.

28:04.000 --> 28:04.800
I understand.

28:05.680 --> 28:06.280
Thank you,

28:06.920 --> 28:07.450
Xiaolan.

28:08.750 --> 28:09.440
Thank you

28:10.410 --> 28:12.810
for being willing to
be compatible with me.

28:17.960 --> 28:19.440
Sometimes I do wonder—

28:19.920 --> 28:20.880
why Zhou Cheng?

28:21.550 --> 28:22.150
Of course,

28:22.830 --> 28:24.920
good looks are certainly one reason.

28:25.790 --> 28:27.050
But more importantly,

28:27.880 --> 28:29.160
he's willing to communicate,

28:29.160 --> 28:30.270
knows how to be understanding,

28:30.270 --> 28:31.640
and can control his emotions.

28:31.640 --> 28:33.370
This kind of sound personality

28:33.400 --> 28:34.860
and enlightened mindset,

28:34.960 --> 28:36.220
even decades from now,

28:36.680 --> 28:38.340
will still be rare qualities.

28:41.750 --> 28:42.270
But

28:43.400 --> 28:44.800
will your parents agree?

28:50.510 --> 28:51.310
I don't agree.

28:52.200 --> 28:53.920
Everyone else is trying to
get to Jingcheng,

28:53.920 --> 28:55.000
but you two insist on heading outward.

28:55.000 --> 28:55.750
Why?

28:56.070 --> 28:57.400
Is the path we parents planned for you

28:57.400 --> 28:58.330
not good enough?

28:58.480 --> 28:59.880
Zhou Cheng goes to
the Political and Legal Affairs Commission,

28:59.880 --> 29:01.110
and Xiaolan goes to the Design Institute.

29:01.110 --> 29:03.040
It matches your majors perfectly.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.400
Your mother is right.

29:04.880 --> 29:06.070
It's not like Jingcheng doesn't have

29:06.070 --> 29:07.750
suitable workplaces for you two.

29:07.750 --> 29:09.680
Why must you go to Shengcheng?

29:12.880 --> 29:14.810
When I first started studying law,

29:15.110 --> 29:15.590
I thought a

29:15.590 --> 29:16.750
perfect legal world

29:17.160 --> 29:19.020
should be built from the top down.

29:19.880 --> 29:20.400
Later,

29:21.270 --> 29:23.590
after learning about more real life cases,

29:23.590 --> 29:25.190
I began to think more and more

29:25.720 --> 29:28.180
about how to put legal ideals
into practice.

29:29.440 --> 29:31.070
When I went to Shengcheng this time,

29:31.070 --> 29:31.680
I actually went with

29:31.680 --> 29:33.080
these questions in mind.

29:34.160 --> 29:35.420
Although I dare not say

29:35.920 --> 29:37.250
I have found the answer,

29:38.110 --> 29:40.030
Senior Wu's Zhiyuan Law Firm

29:40.790 --> 29:42.190
is a worthwhile attempt.

29:44.970 --> 29:46.240
Senior, what made you decide

29:46.240 --> 29:48.770
to leave the court
and start your own law firm?

29:52.070 --> 29:53.720
Maybe it was out of

29:53.920 --> 29:54.680
some self-important

29:54.680 --> 29:56.810
sense of responsibility to the times.

29:57.750 --> 29:59.640
This may sound a bit grandiose,

30:00.440 --> 30:01.840
but it's truly how I feel.

30:04.960 --> 30:05.400
Look.

30:13.960 --> 30:14.790
We're lucky to be born in

30:14.790 --> 30:15.680
such an era.

30:16.400 --> 30:17.400
And having undergone so many years of

30:17.400 --> 30:18.460
higher education,

30:19.480 --> 30:20.350
we should shoulder

30:20.350 --> 30:21.950
heavier responsibilities.

30:22.830 --> 30:24.070
Our country establishing
the Shengcheng Special Zone

30:24.070 --> 30:25.530
is a brand new experiment.

30:26.750 --> 30:29.750
Everyone is crossing the river
by feeling for stones.

30:31.680 --> 30:33.830
Shengcheng is at the forefront of
opening up.

30:33.830 --> 30:35.240
There are more people there,

30:35.240 --> 30:36.040
more passion,

30:36.400 --> 30:37.600
and more complexity.

30:37.790 --> 30:38.880
It needs law students like us

30:38.880 --> 30:40.480
to push it forward together.

30:40.580 --> 30:41.980
Senior Wu said something

30:42.070 --> 30:43.270
that really moved me.

30:44.070 --> 30:44.680
He said,

30:45.480 --> 30:46.030
a case

30:46.750 --> 30:48.510
doesn't just concern one person—

30:48.510 --> 30:50.170
it concerns an entire family.

30:51.550 --> 30:53.070
I want to stay in Shengcheng

30:53.070 --> 30:54.670
to work on more diverse cases

30:55.070 --> 30:57.400
and interact with more different people.

30:58.270 --> 30:58.830
This is why

30:58.830 --> 30:59.750
I want to

30:59.750 --> 31:01.680
choose Shengcheng at this moment.

31:02.030 --> 31:02.790
To first build a

31:02.790 --> 31:04.550
better Shengcheng Special Zone,

31:04.550 --> 31:05.400
and then build a

31:05.400 --> 31:06.270
better China.

31:07.160 --> 31:08.550
I should contribute

31:08.550 --> 31:09.880
in whatever way I can.

31:12.400 --> 31:13.720
Well said, Cheng!

31:13.790 --> 31:14.450
I'll go too!

31:14.480 --> 31:15.400
Wei, sit down.

31:16.160 --> 31:17.360
Don't cause trouble.

31:20.000 --> 31:20.590
It seems

31:21.960 --> 31:23.350
you have really thought carefully

31:23.350 --> 31:24.350
about this issue.

31:26.550 --> 31:27.400
This matter

31:27.640 --> 31:28.900
is not wrong in itself.

31:29.880 --> 31:31.160
That you have such ambition,

31:31.160 --> 31:32.090
your mother and I

31:32.550 --> 31:34.160
are very gratified.

31:34.900 --> 31:36.970
I believe your dream of practicing law

31:36.970 --> 31:38.910
can be realized

31:38.940 --> 31:40.640
in both Jingcheng and Shengcheng.

31:40.640 --> 31:41.500
But Zhou Cheng,

31:42.030 --> 31:43.960
you have to answer me one question.

31:44.160 --> 31:46.090
You insist on going to Shengcheng—

31:46.200 --> 31:47.600
is it because of Xiaolan?

31:47.790 --> 31:48.240
Yes.

31:51.310 --> 31:51.830
But it's also for

31:51.830 --> 31:52.790
my own ideals.

31:56.070 --> 31:57.930
I want to be with the person I love,

31:58.480 --> 31:59.740
striving for our youth

31:59.920 --> 32:01.320
and our ideals together.

32:07.790 --> 32:08.590
Go ahead then.

32:09.830 --> 32:10.690
Go give it a try.

32:11.050 --> 32:12.250
I hope you can find

32:12.270 --> 32:13.400
the future you want.

32:18.200 --> 32:19.310
Let's also wish them

32:19.310 --> 32:20.440
a happy graduation.

32:22.130 --> 32:22.990
Thank you, Dad.

32:23.930 --> 32:25.530
We'll definitely work hard.

32:27.550 --> 32:29.030
You kids.

32:29.550 --> 32:30.640
Do you think going out to venture

32:30.640 --> 32:31.830
is that easy?

32:32.680 --> 32:33.350
Mrs. Guan.

32:33.920 --> 32:34.720
The reason we have the courage

32:34.720 --> 32:36.110
to venture out

32:36.920 --> 32:38.520
is precisely because we know

32:38.830 --> 32:40.590
that our elders have our backs.

32:43.960 --> 32:45.030
Thank you, Mrs. Guan

32:45.030 --> 32:46.560
and Mr. Zhou, for your care.

32:47.440 --> 32:47.900
Come on.

32:50.440 --> 32:51.590
Come on. Cheers.

32:59.750 --> 33:00.610
Just like that,

33:00.750 --> 33:01.350
Zhou Cheng

33:01.720 --> 33:02.270
and I

33:02.590 --> 33:04.590
both said goodbye to being students

33:04.920 --> 33:06.680
and embarked on our own new challenges

33:06.680 --> 33:07.240
in life.

33:07.240 --> 33:09.200
Ready? Three, two, one.

33:14.000 --> 33:14.550
Xiaolan.

33:18.000 --> 33:19.160
Chen Qing?

33:19.220 --> 33:20.400
When are you taking
your graduation photos?

33:20.400 --> 33:21.680
We took them last week.

33:22.400 --> 33:24.200
Xiaolan, I came to tell you

33:24.400 --> 33:26.000
that I've been selected for
government-sponsored study abroad.

33:26.000 --> 33:27.480
I'm going to the UK next week.

33:27.480 --> 33:28.350
To the UK?

33:28.920 --> 33:29.680
That's great.

33:29.680 --> 33:31.080
Still studying finance?

33:31.550 --> 33:32.240
What about you?

33:32.240 --> 33:33.900
Are you staying in Jingcheng?

33:34.790 --> 33:37.050
Zhou Cheng and I plan to go to Shengcheng.

33:42.350 --> 33:43.000
Then...

33:44.550 --> 33:45.810
I wish you all the best.

33:46.920 --> 33:48.180
All the best to you too.

33:55.000 --> 33:55.400
Hello.

33:55.640 --> 33:56.400
May I ask,

33:56.750 --> 33:57.830
is there a lady named Liu Fen

33:57.830 --> 33:59.480
staying here?

33:59.880 --> 34:00.680
Just a moment.

34:02.310 --> 34:04.270
She's on the second floor, Room 202.

34:04.270 --> 34:04.870
Thank you.

34:08.230 --> 34:08.630
Mayor,

34:08.880 --> 34:09.550
got it.

34:10.230 --> 34:10.710
Ms. Liu

34:10.960 --> 34:11.710
is just upstairs.

34:11.710 --> 34:12.239
Room 202.

34:13.230 --> 34:14.159
Comrade Liu Fen.

34:15.360 --> 34:16.230
Mr. Tang?

34:20.110 --> 34:21.040
Why are you here?

34:22.110 --> 34:22.960
Haven't you felt like
you were missing something

34:22.960 --> 34:24.630
these past few days?

34:27.280 --> 34:28.360
What do you mean?

34:30.330 --> 34:31.080
Your watch.

34:31.670 --> 34:33.199
You left it at the hospital.

34:38.630 --> 34:39.590
I forgot.

34:39.880 --> 34:40.480
Thank you.

34:40.630 --> 34:41.480
You're welcome.

34:41.480 --> 34:42.280
If anyone should be saying thanks,

34:42.280 --> 34:43.030
it's me.

34:44.670 --> 34:46.000
How are you feeling now?

34:46.400 --> 34:47.600
I'm recovering well—

34:47.630 --> 34:49.190
fit as a fiddle now.

34:49.920 --> 34:50.650
That's good.

34:51.000 --> 34:52.110
With your condition,

34:52.110 --> 34:52.840
you need to take care of yourself.

34:52.840 --> 34:54.370
Have more millet porridge.

34:54.480 --> 34:54.880
Okay.

34:55.760 --> 34:56.480
The millet porridge

34:56.480 --> 34:57.480
you made last time

34:57.550 --> 34:58.790
was arguably the best

34:59.000 --> 35:00.330
I've ever had in my life.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.010
Are you heading out?

35:04.030 --> 35:06.010
Xiaolan wants to come to Shengcheng.

35:06.010 --> 35:07.550
We can't stay in a hotel forever,

35:07.550 --> 35:09.030
so we thought we'd go look at some houses.

35:09.030 --> 35:09.550
True.

35:09.760 --> 35:10.670
Living here

35:10.800 --> 35:12.130
can be quite expensive.

35:14.590 --> 35:16.320
My brother is here to pick me up.

35:16.720 --> 35:17.550
That's your brother?

35:17.550 --> 35:17.960
Yes.

35:19.400 --> 35:20.860
He has a head for business.

35:21.070 --> 35:22.760
He even printed the company name

35:21.900 --> 35:23.310
[Yuanhui Decoration]

35:22.920 --> 35:23.760
on his van.

35:24.320 --> 35:25.630
It was Xiaolan's idea.

35:26.760 --> 35:27.840
I'll get going then.

35:27.840 --> 35:28.170
Okay.

35:28.280 --> 35:28.760
Goodbye.

35:28.760 --> 35:29.280
Bye.

35:31.480 --> 35:32.410
Comrade Liu Fen.

35:39.400 --> 35:41.000
I want to thank you properly.

35:41.630 --> 35:43.360
Do you have time some other day?

35:43.840 --> 35:44.880
I'd like to buy you dinner.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.610
Is that okay?

35:48.400 --> 35:48.880
Sure.

35:49.710 --> 35:51.040
Let's do it another day.

35:51.070 --> 35:51.480
Okay.

35:51.670 --> 35:52.200
Alright.

35:52.550 --> 35:53.080
Goodbye.

35:53.400 --> 35:53.930
Goodbye.

35:58.480 --> 35:58.960
Bye.

36:04.550 --> 36:05.030
Mayor.

36:05.880 --> 36:06.880
I'll go get the car.

36:06.880 --> 36:07.280
Okay.

36:11.760 --> 36:12.400
Hui'e!

36:13.010 --> 36:14.520
I forgot a small bag.

36:14.550 --> 36:16.150
Bring it down in a bit.

36:16.920 --> 36:17.400
Okay.

36:31.710 --> 36:32.070
Here.

36:32.250 --> 36:32.910
Let me, Mom.

36:40.320 --> 36:40.710
Mom.

36:42.110 --> 36:43.510
You're going so far away.

36:44.550 --> 36:45.960
Coming back during holidays

36:45.960 --> 36:47.690
would be really inconvenient.

36:48.230 --> 36:49.440
Once I've made some money,

36:49.440 --> 36:51.570
I'll take you to Shengcheng for a trip.

36:53.710 --> 36:55.240
Let us know when you arrive.

36:58.590 --> 36:59.850
Don't worry. Alright.

37:01.630 --> 37:02.110
Come on, get in the car.

37:02.110 --> 37:03.170
Alright, alright.

37:03.320 --> 37:04.520
-Go on.
-I'm off then.

37:06.280 --> 37:07.510
Treat Xiaolan well.

37:08.700 --> 37:09.400
Don't worry.

37:09.400 --> 37:10.260
Go back inside.

37:11.710 --> 37:12.320
Cheng.

37:12.480 --> 37:12.960
Cheng!

37:13.230 --> 37:14.800
I'm going to Shengcheng too.

37:14.800 --> 37:15.730
Why are you here?

37:15.920 --> 37:16.800
I've thought it through.

37:16.800 --> 37:17.920
If I stay at that job,

37:17.920 --> 37:18.720
I'll rot away.

37:20.920 --> 37:21.930
Did you tell Second Uncle?

37:21.930 --> 37:23.770
I did! Of course.

37:23.800 --> 37:24.280
Let's go. Come on.

37:24.280 --> 37:25.440
Did your parents agree?

37:25.440 --> 37:26.590
They agreed. They did.

37:26.590 --> 37:27.480
Don't worry, Auntie.

37:27.480 --> 37:28.630
Let's go. Get on.

37:28.840 --> 37:29.500
Get on then.

37:30.830 --> 37:31.960
We're leaving, Mom.

37:32.070 --> 37:33.510
Look out for each other,

37:33.510 --> 37:34.070
Wei.

37:34.110 --> 37:34.670
Don't worry, Auntie.

37:34.670 --> 37:35.400
Don't worry, Mom.

37:35.400 --> 37:36.510
Take care.

37:36.880 --> 37:37.610
I'm off, Mom.

37:43.400 --> 37:44.000
Be careful. Easy.

37:44.000 --> 37:45.110
It's okay. It's okay.

37:45.110 --> 37:46.510
Beer, drinks, peanuts, sunflower seeds.

37:46.510 --> 37:47.400
Anyone need anything?

37:47.400 --> 37:47.800
Hello.

37:48.450 --> 37:50.330
We'll have 3 bottles of soda.

37:50.360 --> 37:52.190
And a bag of sunflower seeds, please.

37:52.190 --> 37:52.750
How much?

37:52.800 --> 37:53.360
You pay.

37:53.550 --> 37:54.280
One twenty in total.

37:54.280 --> 37:55.610
I'll get it. I'll get it.

37:57.070 --> 37:58.280
Beer, drinks, peanuts, sunflower seeds.

37:58.280 --> 37:59.540
Anyone need anything?

38:00.510 --> 38:01.510
Tell me the truth.

38:01.800 --> 38:03.520
Did Second Uncle really agree?

38:03.520 --> 38:04.320
Agree to what?

38:04.320 --> 38:05.800
I didn't even tell him.

38:05.920 --> 38:06.510
If I had told him,

38:06.510 --> 38:08.030
he definitely wouldn't have agreed.

38:08.030 --> 38:09.440
Why should I listen to him?

38:09.440 --> 38:11.640
Young people need to go out and venture.

38:12.960 --> 38:14.280
But then again,

38:14.480 --> 38:15.150
I'm not like

38:15.150 --> 38:16.320
you and Xiaolan,

38:16.400 --> 38:17.840
both educated and smart.

38:18.280 --> 38:19.360
When we get to Shengcheng...

38:19.360 --> 38:19.800
What,

38:20.320 --> 38:21.550
the train just started,

38:21.550 --> 38:22.720
and you're already regretting it?

38:22.720 --> 38:23.680
I'm not.

38:23.710 --> 38:24.670
No matter what happens, it's better than

38:24.670 --> 38:26.400
rotting away in that company.

38:27.070 --> 38:28.000
But Xiaolan,

38:28.480 --> 38:29.840
do you think

38:29.840 --> 38:31.030
I'm really stupid, acting like this?

38:31.030 --> 38:31.630
Not at all.

38:32.050 --> 38:33.380
I think you're amazing.

38:33.480 --> 38:34.140
Very brave.

38:34.510 --> 38:36.310
Much braver than I was back then.

38:36.550 --> 38:37.000
See?

38:37.030 --> 38:39.180
Xiaolan really knows
how to encourage people.

38:39.180 --> 38:40.480
But when it comes to bravery,

38:40.480 --> 38:42.030
Xiaolan is still second to none.

38:42.030 --> 38:42.960
Our Xiaolan

38:43.150 --> 38:44.670
has both brains and guts.

38:47.880 --> 38:50.010
Come on, let's put our hands together.

38:51.280 --> 38:53.080
Here's to a successful venture.

38:53.230 --> 38:54.800
To success!

38:57.630 --> 38:58.710
By the way, Xiaolan,

38:58.710 --> 38:59.880
after we arrive,

38:59.880 --> 39:00.800
do we have any

39:01.360 --> 39:02.290
business plans?

39:02.670 --> 39:04.840
Business plans...

39:06.920 --> 39:07.440
Step 1:

39:07.840 --> 39:09.140
find a place to live first.

39:09.140 --> 39:11.140
Come on, let me show you the balcony.

39:12.550 --> 39:13.710
It's very nice here.

39:16.030 --> 39:16.440
Look.

39:16.780 --> 39:17.840
Isn't it spacious?

39:18.910 --> 39:19.970
You two, come here.

39:20.550 --> 39:21.590
That thing you mentioned just now,

39:21.590 --> 39:22.320
the law firm—

39:22.810 --> 39:23.590
it's right over there.

39:23.590 --> 39:24.760
Just keep walking straight,

39:24.760 --> 39:26.620
and it's the second one at the end.

39:28.710 --> 39:29.310
Is it okay?

39:29.320 --> 39:30.320
Is this room okay?

39:31.210 --> 39:32.010
Isn't it nice?

39:32.400 --> 39:33.550
Pretty good to me. What do you think?

39:33.550 --> 39:34.400
I'm okay with it.

39:34.400 --> 39:35.920
Alright, we'll take it then.

39:35.920 --> 39:36.250
Okay.

39:36.280 --> 39:37.590
Then let's go down and sign the contract.

39:37.590 --> 39:37.880
Okay.

39:37.880 --> 39:38.320
Okay.

39:40.030 --> 39:41.230
This courtyard is nice, isn't it?

39:41.230 --> 39:41.960
Pretty good.

39:42.000 --> 39:43.280
Spacious and clean.

39:43.630 --> 39:44.110
Alright.

39:44.110 --> 39:45.310
We'll stay here then.

39:47.440 --> 39:48.120
Granny Yu.

39:48.630 --> 39:49.880
We'll rent

39:49.880 --> 39:50.960
the two rooms upstairs.

39:50.960 --> 39:51.550
As for the courtyard,

39:51.550 --> 39:53.400
I might store some goods here sometimes,

39:53.400 --> 39:54.530
but not for too long.

39:54.840 --> 39:56.400
How much is the rent?

39:58.110 --> 39:59.840
How many people will live here?

40:00.000 --> 40:00.480
Two.

40:00.710 --> 40:01.710
Just my mom and me.

40:03.880 --> 40:05.590
If you want to rent my rooms,

40:05.920 --> 40:07.510
you must follow my rules.

40:07.880 --> 40:08.360
First,

40:08.800 --> 40:10.510
only the two of you can live here.

40:10.510 --> 40:12.880
No other men or women

40:13.760 --> 40:14.490
are allowed.

40:14.710 --> 40:15.190
Second,

40:15.710 --> 40:18.440
no loud noises in the courtyard.

40:18.670 --> 40:19.280
Third,

40:20.000 --> 40:22.190
you can use the kitchen and the courtyard,

40:22.190 --> 40:22.800
but

40:23.400 --> 40:25.400
the rent must be paid every 6 months.

40:25.710 --> 40:26.590
Every 6 months?

40:27.360 --> 40:28.230
Who are you?

40:29.800 --> 40:30.880
This is my uncle.

40:30.880 --> 40:32.150
He might drop by sometimes

40:32.150 --> 40:33.030
to visit us.

40:33.360 --> 40:34.420
He won't live here.

40:37.030 --> 40:38.360
It'll be 50 yuan a month.

40:38.550 --> 40:39.810
And most importantly,

40:40.880 --> 40:43.140
do not enter my room without permission.

40:43.150 --> 40:44.000
Do not touch

40:45.000 --> 40:45.760
my stuff.

40:46.400 --> 40:46.920
Also,

40:47.480 --> 40:48.150
we are only

40:48.150 --> 40:49.920
landlord and tenants.

40:50.070 --> 40:51.190
If it's not necessary,

40:51.190 --> 40:52.720
don't try to get close to me.

40:52.880 --> 40:54.480
That's all the rules for now.

40:54.590 --> 40:55.440
"For now"?

40:55.440 --> 40:56.070
Do you

40:57.360 --> 40:58.030
agree?

40:58.480 --> 40:58.960
We do.

40:59.590 --> 41:00.190
We agree.

41:00.480 --> 41:01.280
We'll rent it.

41:02.400 --> 41:03.460
Please be careful.

41:05.960 --> 41:06.840
What time is it?

41:08.510 --> 41:09.310
Five o'clock.

41:10.280 --> 41:11.610
It's already 5 o'clock?

41:17.510 --> 41:19.190
Where is this old lady going?

41:20.070 --> 41:21.400
I heard from the agent

41:21.400 --> 41:22.400
that this old lady usually

41:22.400 --> 41:24.000
sweeps the streets nearby.

41:24.030 --> 41:25.280
She has such a big house

41:25.280 --> 41:26.230
and charges such high rent,

41:26.230 --> 41:27.560
yet she sweeps streets?

41:28.280 --> 41:30.280
She's got plenty of rules too.

41:30.510 --> 41:32.440
She's quite an eccentric old lady.

41:32.580 --> 41:34.260
To have such a big courtyard

41:34.320 --> 41:36.070
and speak without an accent,

41:36.450 --> 41:37.710
she must be from a prestigious family,

41:37.710 --> 41:39.070
educated and worldly.

41:39.630 --> 41:41.890
It's normal for her to be a bit eccentric.

41:41.920 --> 41:43.450
She looks pretty kind to me.

41:44.280 --> 41:45.920
Relationships are built over time.

41:45.920 --> 41:46.510
I'm sure

41:46.670 --> 41:47.760
we can win her over.

41:50.440 --> 41:52.070
The housing problem is solved.

41:52.070 --> 41:52.720
Next,

41:53.070 --> 41:54.720
step 2 of starting a business:

41:54.720 --> 41:55.920
getting communication devices.

41:55.920 --> 41:56.280
Right.

41:56.280 --> 41:56.800
Then press down.

41:56.800 --> 41:58.230
See? It works, right?

41:58.920 --> 41:59.970
Great. This is great.

41:59.970 --> 42:00.710
It'll be convenient from now on.

42:00.710 --> 42:01.320
Xiaolan.

42:01.670 --> 42:03.000
This tiny gadget

42:03.000 --> 42:03.690
is so expensive.

42:03.690 --> 42:04.800
Why do we have to buy it?

42:04.800 --> 42:09.130
♪ Along the long road ahead,
how much beauty awaits ♪

42:05.320 --> 42:07.400
Communication is the bridge to everything.

42:07.400 --> 42:09.000
If you reply faster than others

42:09.000 --> 42:09.710
or receive information

42:09.160 --> 42:12.750
♪ I'll take time to appreciate it all ♪

42:09.710 --> 42:10.710
ahead of them,

42:11.000 --> 42:12.600
you can seize the advantage.

42:13.110 --> 42:14.030
I remember the three of us

42:13.610 --> 42:17.510
♪ Why pause and look back? ♪

42:14.030 --> 42:15.230
had consecutive numbers.

42:15.230 --> 42:17.280
Those two have couple numbers.

42:17.510 --> 42:18.480
Why are you getting involved?

42:18.070 --> 42:21.340
♪ My heart feels so confused ♪

42:18.920 --> 42:21.110
B-But consecutive numbers
are easier to remember, right?

42:21.110 --> 42:22.120
Sis Bai, why don't you
get a new number too?

42:21.940 --> 42:25.810
♪ Silently, I watch the clouds
drift in the sky ♪

42:22.150 --> 42:23.320
So the four of us
can have consecutive numbers.

42:23.320 --> 42:24.800
I've had this number
for a year and a half.

42:24.800 --> 42:25.440
If I change it now,

42:25.440 --> 42:26.760
people won't be able to reach me.

42:26.480 --> 42:30.920
♪ Just like you and I,
our ambitions reach far and wide ♪

42:27.800 --> 42:29.320
Besides clipping this on the waist,

42:29.320 --> 42:30.800
can we clip it somewhere else?

42:30.800 --> 42:31.920
Why don't you clip it on your bangs
as a hairpin?

42:30.950 --> 42:34.910
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

42:31.920 --> 42:32.470
Go away.

42:33.150 --> 42:34.210
Alright, alright.

42:34.400 --> 42:34.930
Xiaolan.

42:35.030 --> 42:35.440
Cheng.

42:35.510 --> 42:36.110
Let's clip them on together.

42:35.570 --> 42:40.130
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

42:36.760 --> 42:37.960
Clip.

42:38.760 --> 42:40.000
With these pagers on,

42:40.000 --> 42:40.960
now we should walk...

42:40.150 --> 42:43.380
♪ I hope to wander joyfully with you ♪

42:41.150 --> 42:42.230
Like this.

42:44.140 --> 42:49.340
♪ Hand in hand, exploring strange lands ♪

42:48.710 --> 42:50.190
Step 3 of starting a business:

42:50.190 --> 42:51.110
stay grounded

42:51.510 --> 42:52.920
and start with the tasks at hand.
